 between size and each of the echolocation parameters.\nConclusions\u2002 The incorporation of Bayesian statistics based on large-scale simulations could be helpful for answering macroevolutionary patterns related to the coevolution of traits in bats and other taxonomic groups.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Castro, Mario G.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Amado, Talita Ferreira", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Olalla-T\u00e1rraga, Miguel \u00c1.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/b703b84da20efbfce36f100dac864c45", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/4054d28644e5c33ad0bcf33be44a2e16c850969da845f241987b636c8aaba707", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/XE5GECBK", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/XE5GECBK", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/75734b587c6d2f4734f944ec1d70173f!/b106504-109062", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1", "pages": "44", "title": "BMC Ecology and Evolution", "volume": "24"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/b703b84da20efbfce36f100dac864c45"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:XE5GECBK"}, {"identifier": "10.1186/s12862-024-02231-4"}], "communities": [{"i